                            <head>No. 442<lb/><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                            <p>Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CHURCHILLWS1">Churchill</persName> and President <persName corresp="#p_EISENHOWER1">Eisenhower</persName> met in Washington
                                June 25–29, to discuss problems of mutual concern. For documentation
                                on their meetings, see <ref target="#d454">Documents 454</ref>
                                ff.</p>
